ActionResult.SpecialNote: Can also be used in non-generic form, in such it uses SupportURL and SupportTitle
ActionResult.Description: Generic response type for calls that return a result and a reason for failure

Fields.Name: Status
Fields.Description: true if successful, false if not

Fields.Name: Timestamp
Fields.Description: The timestamp of the console entry

Fields.Name: Source
Fields.Description: The source of the console entry

Fields.Name: SourceId
Fields.Description: The ID of the message's source, eg from a player/user

Fields.Name: Type
Fields.Description: The type of the console entry

Fields.Name: Contents
Fields.Description: The contents of the console entry

Fields.Name: DisplayName
Fields.Description: The display name of the endpoint

ApplicationState.Description: Represents the state of an instance's application

Fields.Name: PreStart
Fields.Description: The server is performing some first-time-start configuration.

Fields.Name: Configuring
Fields.Description: The server is performing some first-time-start configuration.

Fields.Name: Restarting
Fields.Description: Server is in the middle of stopping, but once shutdown has finished it will automatically restart.

Fields.Name: Sleeping
Fields.Description: The application should be able to be resumed quickly if using this state. Otherwise use Stopped.

Fields.Name: Waiting
Fields.Description: The application is waiting for some external service/application to respond/become available.

Fields.Name: AwaitingUserInput
Fields.Description: Used during installation, means that some user input is required to complete setup (authentication etc).

Fields.Name: Indeterminate
Fields.Description: The state is unknown, or doesn't apply (for modules that don't start an external process)

Fields.Name: Daemon
Fields.Description: Whether the instance is a daemon

Fields.Name: ExcludeFromFirewall
Fields.Description: Whether the instance is excluded from the firewall

Fields.Name: IsContainerInstance
Fields.Description: Whether the instance is a container instance

Fields.Name: UseHostModeNetwork
Fields.Description: Whether the container uses host mode network

Fields.Name: DockerNetworkIsHostMode
Fields.Description: Whether the Docker network is in host mode

Fields.Name: IsDirectory
Fields.Description: Whether the file is a directory

Fields.Name: IsVirtualDirectory
Fields.Description: Whether the file is a virtual directory

Fields.Name: IsArchive
Fields.Description: Whether the file is an archive

Fields.Name: IsExcludedFromBackups
Fields.Description: Whether the file is excluded from backups

RemoteInstanceState.Description: Represents the state of a remote instance

Fields.Name: CanCreate
Fields.Description: Whether the instance can be created

Fields.Name: CreatesInContainers
Fields.Description: Whether the instance creates in containers

Fields.Name: IsLDAPUser
Fields.Description: Whether the user is an LDAP user

LicenceInfo.Description: A struct to represent the object returned by Core#ActivateAMPLicence(Guid, Boolean)

LoginResponse.Description: Type for the result of Core.Login

StatusResponse.Description: Type for the result of Core.GetStatus

PushedMessage.Description: Type for API.Core.GetUpdates#Messages[i] (along with WS keep alive)

Fields.Name: AgeMinutes
Fields.Description: The age of the message in minutes

TaskState.Description: Represents the state of a task

Fields.Name: HideFromUI
Fields.Description: Whether the task is hidden from the UI

Fields.Name: FastDismiss
Fields.Description: Whether the task can be dismissed quickly

Fields.Name: DontPropagate
Fields.Description: Whether the task should not propagate

Fields.Name: IsDelayedOpen
Fields.Description: Whether the port is delayed open

Fields.Name: IsDelayedOpen
Fields.Description: Whether the port is delayed open

Fields.Name: ConsoleEntries
Fields.Description: The console entries of the server

ModuleInfo.Description: A struct to represent the object returned by the Core.GetModuleInfo() method

Fields.Name: SupportsSleep
Fields.Description: Whether the module supports sleep mode

Fields.Name: RequiresFullLoad
Fields.Description: Whether the module requires a full load

RemoteTargetInfo.Description: Information about a remote target, returned by ADSModule#GetTargetInfo()

Fields.Name: DeploysInContainers
Fields.Description: Whether the target deploys in containers

UpdateInfo.Description: A struct to represent the object returned by the Core.GetUpdateInfo() method

Fields.Name: ReleaseNotesURL
Fields.Description: The URL to the release notes

Fields.Name: PatchOnly
Fields.Description: Whether the update is a patch

Fields.Name: Deferred
Fields.Description: Whether the selection source is deferred

Fields.Name: MustValidate
Fields.Description: Whether the selection source must validate

Fields.Name: EnumValuesAreDeferred
Fields.Description: Whether the enum values are deferred

Fields.Name: IsProvisionSpec
Fields.Description: Whether the setting is a provision spec

Fields.Name: AlwaysAllowRead
Fields.Description: Whether the setting is always allowed to be read

Fields.Name: RequiresRestart
Fields.Description: Whether the setting requires a restart

Fields.Name: CloneRoleIntoUser
Fields.Description: Whether to clone the role into the user

Fields.Name: IsServiceSpec
Fields.Description: Whether the spec is a service spec

ApplicationSpecSummary.Description: A summary of an application spec
